### 6. Verify Contract List for the Employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/contracts?employeeId={{employeeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
# response of contract list for the employee
# {
#     "statusCode": 200,
#     "message": [
#         {
#             "success": true,
#             "contracts": [
